text: Cheryl Lynn (11 March 1957) is an American R&B;, disco and pop singer who was most popular in the late 1970s to early 1980s. She is famous for her popular single "Got to be Real". Cheryl Lynn was born in Los Angeles. Category:American R&B; singers Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Singers from Los Angeles
title: Cheryl Lynn
